        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": "AniZhuanchangEnd",
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Inside a quiet room, several holographic projections slowly overlap, forming an almost-humanoid figure.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 41,
        "ActionId": 41,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 201,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '500160'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 42,
        "ActionId": 42,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '???', 3: 'Respond accepted. Password authorized. Loading preset—general interaction interface—', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 43,
        "ActionId": 43,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Huaxu', 3: 'The administrator logged in. Welcome, Master Villier.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 44,
        "ActionId": 44,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Hearing Huaxu\\'s usual greetings, the Construct Villier reveals a rare, gentle smile.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 45,
        "ActionId": 45,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 201,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '500150'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 46,
        "ActionId": 46,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Villier', 3: 'You\\'re probably the only one left who\\'d call me \"Villier\"... But that\\'s enough. I don\\'t need someone else to understand who I am.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 47,
        "ActionId": 47,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Huaxu\\'s figure flickers as if thinking about something.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 48,
        "ActionId": 48,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 201,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '500160'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 49,
        "ActionId": 49,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Huaxu', 3: 'The passengers\\' survival rate is, in fact, increasing compared to the simulations done every half an hour after your initial announcement. I want to understand why you did it, Master Villier.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 50,
        "ActionId": 50,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Villier turns on the surveillance system, monitoring the different corners of the Nighter lives.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 51,
        "ActionId": 51,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 201,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '500150'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 52,
        "ActionId": 52,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Villier', 3: 'Huaxu, you still don\\'t fully understand humans... You have to understand them to manipulate them well.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 53,
        "ActionId": 53,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Villier', 3: 'Apart from a few, most people who boarded the Nighter were the working class who struggled under Qu\\'s rules. These seemingly authoritative but extremely pliable rules are in fact an opportunity.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 54,
        "ActionId": 54,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Villier', 3: 'They will welcome our policies with open arms and work tirelessly to earn these \"miles,\" building us exceptional Constructs. Then, one day... I will find a Construct that can become your body.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 55,
        "ActionId": 55,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 201,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '500160'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 56,
        "ActionId": 56,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Huaxu', 3: 'My body...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 57,
        "ActionId": 57,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Villier tries to caress Huaxu\\'s face. Even though he knows the figure before him is just a hologram, he is still disappointed that his touch meets only air.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 58,
        "ActionId": 58,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 201,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '500150'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 59,
        "ActionId": 59,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Villier', 3: 'I once thought not to rely on humans as well... I thought I could build you a perfect body with my own hands.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 60,
        "ActionId": 60,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Villier', 3: 'That was the most flawless mechanoid I\\'d ever built—or so I thought. Even when I tailored it for you, its logic system still failed to adapt to your consciousness, a mind that uses the same architecture of Gestalt.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 61,
        "ActionId": 61,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Villier', 3: 'But it made me realize that only a Construct\\'s M.I.N.D. is ideal for you.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 62,
        "ActionId": 62,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
